data.description: Exquisite 4 bedroom 3.5 bath home located in the quiet gated community Buckhead Park at Lenox of Atlanta! This beautiful home features an open and bright floor plan with tons of natural light and fantastic views. The large family room features a grand stone fireplace and hardwood floors. The kitchen has beautifully cherry-stained cabinets, stone countertops, and stainless appliances with an island. The master has a double-trayed ceiling with a sitting room. The master bath features double vanities with stone counters, a glass-enclosed walk-in shower, a large soaking tub, and walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms are spacious and bright. There are covered porches on each of the 3 levels giving you great views and privacy to enjoy the outdoors. This home has everything you need plus easy access to major highways! Great Schools!
